OL,3,CTeenage girls are less likely to feel
OL,4,Csafe in school than boys, study finds
OL,6,FThe study found that interventions to
OL,7,Fhelp boost pupils' emotional
OL,8,Fengagement with school are needed,
OL,9,Fwith a focus on supporting girls to
OL,10,Ffeel safe.
OL,12,FA pupil's emotional engagement refers
OL,13,Fto their enjoyment of school, their
OL,14,Frelationships with their peers and
OL,15,Fteachers and the extent to which they
OL,16,Ffeel safe and that they belong in
OL,17,Fschool.
